<p><br>에디터에 아래 코드를 복사&amp;붙여넣기 합니다. 그리고 <strong>save</strong>버튼을 눌러 저장합니다.</p>
<h6 id="코드-내용복사붙여넣기"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#코드-내용복사붙여넣기"></a> 코드 내용(복사&amp;붙여넣기)</h6>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> steem = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;steem&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> cron = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;node-cron&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> username = process.env.username;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> wif = process.env.wif;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">reward</span>(<span class="params"></span>) ｛</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">  <span class="title">steem</span>.<span class="title">api</span>.<span class="title">getAccountsAsync</span>(<span class="params">[username]</span>).<span class="title">then</span>(<span class="params"><span class="keyword">function</span>([account]) ｛</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">    <span class="keyword">const</span> ｛ name, reward_vesting_steem, reward_sbd_balance, reward_vesting_balance ｝ = account;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">`Pending Rewards: $｛reward_vesting_steem｝ / $｛reward_sbd_balance｝ / $｛reward_vesting_balance｝`</span>);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(reward_vesting_balance !== <span class="string">&quot;0.000000 VESTS&quot;</span>) ｛</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">      steem.broadcast.claimRewardBalanceAsync(wif, name, <span class="string">&#x27;0.000 STEEM&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;0.000 SBD&#x27;</span>, reward_vesting_balance).then(<span class="keyword">function</span>() ｛</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">        <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">&quot;Rewards Claimed!&quot;</span>);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">      ｝);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">    ｝</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"><span class="function">  ｝</span>)</span>;</span><br><span class="line">｝</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 1시간마다 실행</span></span><br><span class="line">cron.schedule(<span class="string">&#x27;0 */1 * * *&#x27;</span>, reward);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
